8
00:00:34,620 --> 00:00:35,700
ظآزHow beautifulظآز

9
00:00:35,700 --> 00:00:38,860
=Blooms for Her=

10
00:00:38,900 --> 00:00:41,820
=Episode 9=

11
00:00:42,240 --> 00:00:45,200
Are you... worried about him?

12
00:00:58,399 --> 00:01:00,560
Jian, you're overthinking it.

13
00:01:01,320 --> 00:01:03,200
I'm only concerned

14
00:01:03,200 --> 00:01:04,480
because he accidentally

15
00:01:04,480 --> 00:01:06,120
helped me with my plan today.

16
00:01:06,599 --> 00:01:08,359
Murong Jinghe and I

17
00:01:09,239 --> 00:01:11,159
are just business partners.

18
00:01:39,959 --> 00:01:40,760
He was here.

19
00:01:42,239 --> 00:01:43,760
Did he hear everything?

20
00:01:54,680 --> 00:01:57,680
Thank you, Your Highness,
for buying me time.

21
00:01:59,120 --> 00:02:01,200
Why did you take such a desperate gamble

22
00:02:01,200 --> 00:02:02,200
to get close to him?

23
00:02:03,359 --> 00:02:04,480
Do you know what happens

24
00:02:04,599 --> 00:02:06,200
if Murong Xuanlie finds out?

25
00:02:06,200 --> 00:02:08,199
You won't even know how you died.

26
00:02:09,759 --> 00:02:11,319
I have the cure to the poison.

27
00:02:13,879 --> 00:02:15,280
Besides, what I did

28
00:02:15,599 --> 00:02:17,360
was only to finish the mission sooner.

29
00:02:20,039 --> 00:02:21,680
Here's the antidote for the powder.

30
00:02:22,199 --> 00:02:23,639
In his secret room, I also found

31
00:02:23,800 --> 00:02:25,439
(Border Army Supply Withdrawal Record)
his corruption ledger.

32
00:02:25,800 --> 00:02:27,560
(Border Army Supply Withdrawal Record)
It can help you take him down.

33
00:02:27,560 --> 00:02:28,460
(Border Army Supply Withdrawal Record)

34
00:02:29,240 --> 00:02:32,560
This should be enough
to exchange for Su Jian's life, right?

35
00:02:36,400 --> 00:02:37,199
Mission?

36
00:02:38,319 --> 00:02:40,520
So everything I did

37
00:02:42,159 --> 00:02:44,000
was just a transaction?

38
00:02:53,759 --> 00:02:56,319
I went to him because I was afraid
the poison would kill you,

39
00:02:57,280 --> 00:02:59,759
not because of some deal between us.

40
00:02:59,800 --> 00:03:01,000
Do you even understand that?

41
00:03:02,599 --> 00:03:03,879
Thank you for your concern.

42
00:03:05,639 --> 00:03:06,840
I'm deeply grateful.

43
00:03:08,360 --> 00:03:09,159
But...

44
00:03:13,039 --> 00:03:17,479
Between you and me
is just a transaction. That's all.

45
00:03:19,520 --> 00:03:21,120
The antidote and ledger are here.

46
00:03:21,919 --> 00:03:25,520
I believe we're even now.

47
00:03:26,919 --> 00:03:27,719
I should go.

48
00:03:29,020 --> 00:03:31,820
ظآزA celestial bird
brushes the mountain's edgeظآز

49
00:03:33,140 --> 00:03:34,820
ظآزWings of light drift through the airظآز

50
00:03:34,820 --> 00:03:38,500
ظآزLike blossoms that refuse to fadeظآز

51
00:03:39,300 --> 00:03:42,300
ظآزIt asks no right or wrongظآز

52
00:03:42,500 --> 00:03:45,180
ظآزNor fears the turning of fateظآز

53
00:03:46,400 --> 00:03:47,520
Look who's here.

54
00:03:48,360 --> 00:03:49,479
Tell me about it.

55
00:03:50,240 --> 00:03:51,879
Always hanging around His Majesty,

56
00:03:51,879 --> 00:03:52,800
