57
00:03:53,120 --> 00:03:54,400
Take a good look at yourself

58
00:03:54,400 --> 00:03:55,879
and see what you really are.

59
00:03:56,039 --> 00:03:56,759
Exactly.

60
00:03:56,759 --> 00:03:58,400
(Yue Qin)
A Zhao hostage like you

61
00:03:58,400 --> 00:03:59,759
(State of Zhao's Hostage Prince)
is not even worth

62
00:03:59,800 --> 00:04:01,560
as much as a dog in this palace.

63
00:04:09,560 --> 00:04:10,280
Give it back!

64
00:04:10,879 --> 00:04:13,080
It's the only keepsake
my mother left me.

65
00:04:13,080 --> 00:04:14,439
Just a worn-out pouch.

66
00:04:14,719 --> 00:04:17,319
Come take it yourself if you can.

67
00:04:17,639 --> 00:04:18,519
Come on.

68
00:04:18,879 --> 00:04:19,680
Take it.

69
00:04:31,319 --> 00:04:32,120
Come on.

70
00:04:33,199 --> 00:04:33,920
Go ahead.

71
00:04:33,920 --> 00:04:35,160
You worthless trash!

72
00:04:35,800 --> 00:04:36,600
Stop!

73
00:04:50,879 --> 00:04:52,240
- Greetings, Princess Anhe.
- Greetings, Princess Anhe.

74
00:04:52,360 --> 00:04:53,680
Before I summon the guards,

75
00:04:53,920 --> 00:04:54,720
get lost.

76
00:04:55,160 --> 00:04:56,040
- Yes.
- Yes.

